rComments: It is discussion-based every day, so make sure to read.  The only difficult part of the class was when the readings would be too long from the Monday-Wednesday span, but I always caught up because the books are worth it.  Other than that, participate a lot and she's a pretty easy grader and very fun!

Prof. Sobol is one my favorite professors ever.  She is a great lecturer, extremely knowledgeable and passionate about Russian literature, and always willing to provide help if needed.  It was a pleasure take her class on War and Peace.
